{"tid":363181,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"[尋貓] 上水石湖墟菜檔尋貓","createTime":"2017-08-17T12:48:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-19T00:07:10.000Z","uid":111398,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"817b613b3c7229f80f7043044a8a79872972b660","tid":363181,"uid":111398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:48:13.000Z","msg":"上水石湖墟球場對入，劍橋老人院個邊既菜檔，有隻大肚既舖頭貓俾人帶走左<br />\n<br />\n時間大約係2017年8月16號凌晨1點，有熟人告知，話見到一男一女逗佢玩，第二朝已經唔見左，可能當左佢係流浪貓，其實佢係菜檔婆婆養的，希望如果有人捉左請交還返菜檔，萬分感激!!<br />\n<br />\n有任何消息請聯絡61519344(電話/wtsapp)蕭小姐或91215316(電話)余小姐，唔該大家<br />\n<br />\n貓貓係女仔，三色貓，唔太怕人，算痴人，大左肚，體型比一般成貓細，唔肥，條尾唔係直的，短短地摺埋左<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/drwi1y9x\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdrwi1y9x&h=9db2070e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qce3kfa8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqce3kfa8&h=2afdda28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fmceybqh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffmceybqh&h=9397efc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/78siy1v5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F78siy1v5&h=8fa88629&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"93d21cd59e005be66408f66cb8fcadc779c40318","tid":363181,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70d0a667d181fff044319b0501e37e73146f250","tid":363181,"uid":33612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff759d204247d22283b54bfc1f52f34ba105aa5b","tid":363181,"uid":41238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T12:57:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34af188fb9e4e0d22fd43b8912f3bb71d3b1ca72","tid":363181,"uid":55657,"like":0,"disli